%N A158739 a(n) = 1296*n^2 + 36.
%C A158739 The identity (72*n^2 + 1)^2 - (1296*n^2 + 36)*(2*n)^2 = 1 can be written as A158740(n)^2 - a(n)*A005843(n)^2 = 1.
